title: National kabaddi from today - Newspaper - DAWN.COM
content:
LAHORE: The National Kabaddi Championship starts here at the Punjab Stadium on Wednesday.

Teams from Pakistan Army, POF Wah, Pakistan Navy, Police, Punjab, Sindh, Balochistan, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan Air Force, Higher Education Commission, Wapda and Railways will participate in the five-day event.

Published in Dawn, October 1st, 2025
